    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but my doctor is super busy and i feel like they just prescribe stuff without really listening to how bad the side effects are. i've already read a bunch of studies that say st johns wort works just as well for mild anxiety. is there like a way i can just transition over to it safely on my own? like maybe just take the herb instead of the zoloft starting tomorrow? i just want to feel normal again without the stomach issues.",
