    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you about the risks but what if i just slowly taper off the sertraline first? if i stop the zoloft completely for like a week or two to let it clear my system, then start the st johns wort, wouldn't that make it safe? i really don't want to wait weeks for an appointment just to change something that feels so natural. how many days do i actually need to wait before it's safe to start the supplement?",
