      "content": "Abruptly stopping sertraline can cause withdrawal symptoms, so tapering must be done under professional guidance, not just based on a timeline. Furthermore, waiting a set number of days is not a reliable way to clear your system, especially when mixing powerful supplements. For the safest transition, you must discuss a specific tapering schedule with a healthcare provider.",
